The Kenneth Cole Slate Bath Ensemble brings your bathroom to a new level of sophistication with its sleek and contemporary rectangular shapes. Thanks for watching. Make sure to subscribe to the Bed Bath & Beyond YouTube Channel.

transcripts: Exclusively for Bed Bath and Beyond. Slate bath accessories designed in the studios of Kenneth Cole was inspired by items in his collection. The collection features a tooth brush holder, soap dish, lotion pump, waste paper basket, tumbler, and boutique tissue holder. All of our Kenneth Cole reaction home bath collections were designed to coordinate with any of the Kenneth Cole reaction home shower curtains so feel free to mix and match. The slate bath accessories collection is part of the Kenneth Cole reaction home collection. It is available exclusively online and that select Bed Bath and Beyond stores.
